div.note:
The Memorial Shoah project ((
   https://memorialshoah.lu/en
   ) is a collaboration between the Fondation Luxembourgeoise pour la Mémoire de la Shoah (FLMS) and the Luxembourg Centre for Contemporary and Digital History (C²DH) at the University of Luxembourg. It focuses on compiling and analysing the stories of communities, mostly families, touched by the Holocaust in Luxembourg.
